        <p>Agar aapko lagta hai of hair normal from zyada patle ho rahe hain, ya agar daily 100 from zyada hair gir rahe hain, toh dermatologist from milna zaroori hai. Sudden thinning hormonal imbalance ya underlying health condition ka sign ho sakta hai.</p>

